title: Americanflat 8x20 Panoramic Picture Frame in Black - Four 6x4 Photo Frame Openings - Multi Aperture Collage Picture Frame with Horizontal and Vertical Format for Wall and Tabletop
features: Design: Black 8x20 inch (20x51 cm) collage frame with four 6x4 inch (15x10 cm) openings. Use for family portraits and vacation photos. It includes a white bevelled mount. Hanging hardware is provided for easy display in horizontal or vertical format.
Material: Engineered wood picture frames with a polished shatter-resistant glass front that gives a clear view of your pictures and preserves your photographs, cards, and memories.

Quality: Durable, gallery-style picture frames for multiple pictures; the frame's front has clear glass and a sturdy backboard to keep the photos in place; load your photos, cards, and memories easily, quickly, and securely.
Use and Display: Ideal for four 6x4 inch (10x15 cm) pictures with a mount or one 8x20 inch (20x50 cm) panorama picture without a mount; actual mount openings are 3.5x5.5 inches (8.89x13.97 cm).

Protective Packaging: Americanflat has developed exclusive proprietary packaging that safeguards picture frames during transit, ensuring they arrive safely. Order with confidence, click, and add to cart today!
